                            <comment id="15576447" author="dimaspivak" created="Fri, 14 Oct 2016 20:51:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We started seeing this behavior in-house at Cloudera starting with CDH 5.7, when we rebased onto HBase 1.2, though I should note we sometimes saw it with the &lt;tt&gt;calm&lt;/tt&gt; monkey, as well. This would suggest stability problems with the HBase master, though I haven&apos;t opened a separate JIRA as we didn&apos;t get any useful logging to go along with the isolated failures we saw.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
